	int "IRQ_PTP_STAT"
	default 10

	help
	  Enter the priority numbers between 7-13 ONLY.  Others are Reserved.
	  This applies to all the above.  It is not recommended to assign the
	  highest priority number 7 to UART or any other device.

endmenu

